<main id="content" class="content"> <header> <h1 class="title">Who Is My God?</h1>
 <p class="subtitle" role="doc-subtitle">Mar 19, 2017 00:00</p>
</header> <p>
Does my God <br></br>
love only what I love, <br></br>
and hate only what I hate?
</p>

 <p>
If so, then who is my God?
</p>

 <p>
Does my God <br></br>
demand nothing of me <br></br>
that I donâ€™t want to give?
</p>

 <p>
If not, then what value is this grace?
</p>

 <p>
Lead me away from the <br></br>
altar of my convenience, <br></br>
and teach me once again <br></br>
what it means to love you.
</p>

 <p>
 <i>Amen</i>
</p>



